metadata.name: DGFamily Platinum Box #1
metadata.description: By special access only. The Platinum Box is the pinnacle of the DGFamily community, and the most exclusive. It grants all of the privileges of the Gold Box, plus more: access to the rarest drops and most special IRL experiences, including an intimate Dolce&Gabbana offsite. [View more details UNXD](https://drops.unxd.com/dgfamily/)
